These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, cat, guinea-pig
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking lemonade##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is not the person drinking lemonade##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | chinchilla     | rabbit   | guinea-pig | cat |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Beverage         | lemonade  | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate  | juice |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

