 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
 7. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the art-deco house is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
12. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

