.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, dunhill, montecristo
City: venice, rome, miami, berlin
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the montecristo-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Cigar         | bolivar | dunhill  | montecristo     | bluemaster  |
| City     | venice     | miami | berlin | rome     |

