.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, tennis, handball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, musical, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 3. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
10. the fan of indie is not the brazilian##6
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Sport      | lacrosse      | handball  | tennis | swimming        |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | martial-arts   | epic   | musical |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house   | indie    | dubstep      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

