.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, aconite, begonia, zinnia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, cain, bluemaster
 1. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the person who growsrose is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
12. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
13. the cain-smoker is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Flower         | begonia           | rose     | zinnia       | aconite  |
| Cigar   | bluemaster            | cain   | oliveros     | swisher |

