.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, water
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, brazilian, chinese
House: cottage, art-deco, craftsman, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the brazilian is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the cottage house is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the chinese is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the cottage house is not to the left of the dutch##8
 5. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the craftsman house##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the mexican##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the modern house##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Nationality       | dutch      | mexican      | chinese | brazilian |
| House         | modern | craftsman | art-deco     | cottage  |
| Transport   | roller          | jet-ski      | quad-bike     | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
4 different pets are kept: rat, fish, hedgehog, horse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, august, september
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 4. the owner of the horse is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Pet           | rat | fish    | hedgehog | horse    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Birthday   | february   | august      | january         | september     |

 